=head1 NAME

classes/fixedpmcarray.pmc - fixed size array for PMCs only

=head1 DESCRIPTION

This class, FixedPMCArray, implements an array of fixed size, which stores PMCs,
it puts things into Integer, Float, or String PMCs as appropriate

